Viewing on mobile? Watch here . 
LSU running back Leonard Fournette previews the Florida Gators' visit to Tiger Stadium. 
LSU running back, Leonard Fournette, had his 10th 100-yard rushing game of his career vs. South Carolina. LSU is 9-1 when Fournette reaches 100 rushing yards.
